WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 39=

02:02.060 --> 02:02.940
Xiaoxiao.

02:38.070 --> 02:38.910
Thank heavens.

02:39.620 --> 02:40.460
You're still alive.

02:42.140 --> 02:43.350
I don't want you to die.

02:49.580 --> 02:50.420
Got it.

03:07.900 --> 03:09.300
In the end, I still died

03:09.300 --> 03:10.620
for the one I love.

03:40.950 --> 03:41.790
Farewell,

03:45.300 --> 03:46.140
Yan Ke.

04:47.590 --> 04:48.620
It's Miss He.

04:48.670 --> 04:49.510
- Yes.
- Yes.

04:49.860 --> 04:51.470
Miss He won the fight.

04:52.000 --> 04:53.300
Blast it!

04:53.300 --> 04:54.170
We won!

04:54.230 --> 04:55.860
We made it out alive!

04:58.380 --> 04:59.420
We won!

05:00.060 --> 05:01.470
We won!

05:01.550 --> 05:02.400
We won!

05:02.470 --> 05:03.550
We won!

05:08.060 --> 05:09.470
We won.

05:11.110 --> 05:12.350
We won.

05:14.420 --> 05:15.910
We won.

05:16.030 --> 05:19.590
We won!

05:19.990 --> 05:21.150
We won.

05:22.550 --> 05:23.390
Xiaoxiao.

05:30.670 --> 05:31.510
Xiaoxiao.

05:51.590 --> 05:52.430
(It is Xu.)

06:03.740 --> 06:05.230
Did you come to kill me?

06:05.710 --> 06:06.623
North Chong has fallen.

06:07.820 --> 06:08.990
The Cangshen you believed in

06:11.150 --> 06:12.230
was never real.

06:13.260 --> 06:14.790
Yan Ke, who gave you power,

06:15.740 --> 06:17.150
has met annihilation as well.

06:18.350 --> 06:19.380
Even the North soldiers

06:19.380 --> 06:20.230
who trusted only you

06:21.500 --> 06:22.500
were dead because of you.

06:23.790 --> 06:25.060
You have nothing left now.

06:26.180 --> 06:27.260
Nonsense.

06:28.350 --> 06:29.990
I did not cause their deaths.

06:31.790 --> 06:32.940
You killed them.

06:35.180 --> 06:36.910
I'll avenge them on you.

07:24.670 --> 07:26.470
I thought I was going to lose you.

07:30.180 --> 07:31.020
No.

07:32.710 --> 07:34.150
You will never lose me.

08:02.550 --> 08:03.390
Xu.

08:04.030 --> 08:04.870
Xiaoxiao.

08:05.910 --> 08:06.750
I'm back.

08:44.190 --> 08:45.330
The Chong people's privileges

08:45.341 --> 08:46.670
in the 17 Prefectures are revoked.

08:47.470 --> 08:48.756
All lands and houses they seized

08:49.020 --> 08:50.990
must be returned
to Great Liang's people.

08:51.590 --> 08:52.540
Within Liang's borders,

08:53.140 --> 08:54.740
all people are born equal.

08:55.140 --> 08:56.430
None shall serve another people.

08:56.766 --> 08:57.899
People's will shall be loyal

08:58.110 --> 08:58.950
to His Majesty,

08:59.620 --> 09:00.646
(Decree)
as it should be.

09:01.110 --> 09:02.023
This is hereby claimed.

09:02.190 --> 09:04.470
Wonderful. Wonderful.

09:05.660 --> 09:08.420
(Rice Shop)

09:08.430 --> 09:09.270
The Chong foe!

09:52.990 --> 09:54.950
Great Ancestor.

10:13.710 --> 10:14.900
I have not failed your trust.

10:16.470 --> 10:17.540
I've retaken all

10:17.540 --> 10:18.430
of our lost lands.

10:19.430 --> 10:20.663
I now return the military tally

10:20.860 --> 10:21.770
and the marshal's seal

10:22.710 --> 10:23.620
to His Majesty.

10:24.190 --> 10:26.310
You've done an unprecedented feat.

10:26.780 --> 10:27.620
That is high merit.

10:28.110 --> 10:28.950
The people of Liang

10:29.230 --> 10:30.110
will remember it.

10:39.140 --> 10:40.740
You gave up military power so easily?

10:41.310 --> 10:42.740
I never meant to hold an army.

10:43.673 --> 10:44.740
Now that the 17 Prefectures

10:44.740 --> 10:45.620
have been recovered,

10:46.710 --> 10:47.990
I should return military power

10:48.110 --> 10:49.070
to His Majesty.

11:13.950 --> 11:15.109
How much time do I have left?

11:21.470 --> 11:22.380
Just tell me.

11:28.190 --> 11:30.020
When you stop dodging your medicine,

11:30.960 --> 11:32.310
I will tell you.

11:53.180 --> 12:00.540
(Liang)

12:05.310 --> 12:06.190
Is he asleep?

12:09.590 --> 12:11.190
Duan Xu is not doing well.

12:11.900 --> 12:12.740
He...

12:14.740 --> 12:15.950
If he really leaves,

12:17.500 --> 12:18.470
what will you do?

12:27.140 --> 12:28.830
I still have much to do.

12:30.470 --> 12:32.660
Jiang Ai is watching the Void for me,

12:33.710 --> 12:34.900
but her heart is not in it.

12:35.470 --> 12:36.830
In time, she will return it to me.

12:37.830 --> 12:38.670
Also, Chenying

12:39.310 --> 12:40.740
absorbed the Spirits Lantern's power

12:40.740 --> 12:41.580
and became a spirit.

12:42.500 --> 12:43.660
His obsession is to protect.

12:44.310 --> 12:45.500
If he is willing,

12:46.190 --> 12:47.350
perhaps he can take over

12:47.840 --> 12:49.190
my place soon.

12:50.830 --> 12:51.740
I'm not talking

12:51.740 --> 12:53.140
about the Sovereign.

12:54.860 --> 12:55.900
I'm talking

12:58.350 --> 12:59.540
about you.

13:16.620 --> 13:17.460
I don't know.

13:21.380 --> 13:22.860
Perhaps when that day comes,

13:24.350 --> 13:25.230
I will know.

13:42.660 --> 13:43.860
Right now, whenever I think

13:45.500 --> 13:46.900
that Duan Xu may leave me,

13:48.710 --> 13:49.550
I feel

13:52.500 --> 13:53.740
as if time might vanish

13:53.740 --> 13:54.780
into thin air.

13:58.190 --> 13:59.780
I can see so many things

13:59.780 --> 14:00.710
waiting for me to do,

14:05.020 --> 14:06.540
yet I can't see myself.

14:26.180 --> 14:29.620
(Zhaomu Pavilion)

14:38.540 --> 14:39.900
Simu, you are back.

14:41.350 --> 14:42.230
Who is this?

14:43.900 --> 14:45.020
This is my brother, Chenying.

14:45.566 --> 14:47.045
The Spirits Lantern made him a spirit.

14:47.110 --> 14:47.950
He's still very weak.

14:48.350 --> 14:50.260
Lady Jiang Ai, please watch over him.

14:51.110 --> 14:51.950
Also,

14:52.020 --> 14:52.880
please oversee

14:52.900 --> 14:54.140
the Void for a while longer.

14:59.780 --> 15:00.740
With Lady Jiang Ai here,

15:01.620 --> 15:02.460
don't worry.

15:12.660 --> 15:14.470
What obsession brought you here?

15:16.310 --> 15:18.430
I want to protect Xu and Xiaoxiao.

15:19.230 --> 15:21.230
I kept thinking they had not made peace,

15:21.710 --> 15:22.660
and their wishes

15:22.860 --> 15:23.900
have yet to come true.

15:24.990 --> 15:26.260
I had to see them again.

15:27.020 --> 15:27.860
And I had to

15:27.990 --> 15:29.350
make their wishes come true.

15:30.710 --> 15:31.570
Then

15:31.660 --> 15:32.860
I really saw them again.

15:33.780 --> 15:34.620
How lucky.

15:36.470 --> 15:37.500
At such a young age,

15:37.500 --> 15:38.860
you carry such heavy sorrow,

15:38.860 --> 15:40.140
yet you count yourself lucky.

15:42.380 --> 15:43.230
I'm not lucky.

15:44.590 --> 15:45.740
Xu is gravely ill.

15:46.660 --> 15:48.110
Xiaoxiao is hurting too.

15:49.380 --> 15:50.860
But I can't help in the least.

15:52.860 --> 15:53.700
Lady Jiang Ai,

15:54.660 --> 15:56.110
if Xu is gone...

16:00.460 --> 16:02.780
(Tomb of He Yicheng and Siwei)

16:02.780 --> 16:03.620
Old man,

16:05.230 --> 16:06.380
your grudge has been settled.

16:09.590 --> 16:10.430
Are you pleased?

16:21.230 --> 16:22.260
It's been over 400 years.

16:25.230 --> 16:26.740
I am older than you two now.

16:29.860 --> 16:30.700
From now on,

16:32.590 --> 16:34.190
you may have one more neighbor.

16:35.620 --> 16:36.500
After he passes,

16:38.050 --> 16:38.900
I plan to lay him

16:38.900 --> 16:39.990
to rest beside you two.

16:49.780 --> 16:51.350
After you left, I swore

16:54.350 --> 16:56.020
I'd never be left behind again,

16:57.780 --> 16:59.350
and I'd be the one who leaves first.

16:59.420 --> 17:03.340
(Tomb of He Yicheng and Siwei)

17:03.710 --> 17:05.340
But I repeat my mistake again.

17:08.540 --> 17:10.060
I gave him the right

17:11.460 --> 17:12.300
to leave me

17:12.300 --> 17:13.670
before I do.

17:16.780 --> 17:17.780
One day,

17:20.150 --> 17:22.060
I suppose it will break my heart.

17:27.870 --> 17:28.710
And now,

17:29.670 --> 17:30.780
I find myself thinking

17:32.045 --> 17:33.939
that if he left me and vanished
from this world

17:33.950 --> 17:35.300
50 years from now,

17:37.260 --> 17:38.100
it wouldn't be

17:38.100 --> 17:39.470
so impossible to bear.

17:45.260 --> 17:47.390
But I've known him for only 7 years.

17:51.230 --> 17:52.630
It's too short.

17:55.470 --> 17:56.780
Truly, far too short.

18:17.870 --> 18:20.060
But there is no helping it,

18:21.500 --> 18:22.340
is there?

18:48.900 --> 18:53.300
(Youzhou)

19:00.820 --> 19:01.660
All is settled now.

19:02.390 --> 19:03.230
Today, I shall drink

19:03.950 --> 19:04.790
with all of you.

19:05.260 --> 19:06.390
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

19:13.710 --> 19:15.260
I truly never imagined

19:15.740 --> 19:18.020
that after such a brutal battle,

19:18.580 --> 19:19.910
not only did we all survive,

19:20.230 --> 19:22.190
but we also reclaimed
the 17 Prefectures.

19:22.910 --> 19:24.940
My life is worth it.

19:25.060 --> 19:25.900
Worth it indeed.

19:27.060 --> 19:27.910
Han.

19:27.990 --> 19:28.830
Qingsheng.

19:31.390 --> 19:32.665
- Here.
- That we could reclaim

19:32.676 --> 19:33.630
the 17 Prefectures

19:33.870 --> 19:34.780
feels like a dream.

19:39.430 --> 19:41.180
- I still remember
- Marshal Duan.

19:41.630 --> 19:42.470
we entered Liangzhou.

19:44.230 --> 19:45.540
Back then, you even suspected

19:45.540 --> 19:46.380
I was a spy.

19:48.150 --> 19:49.089
Now that I think of it,

19:49.100 --> 19:50.060
he did look like a spy.

19:51.190 --> 19:52.030
Come on.

19:52.470 --> 19:53.340
Cheers.

19:53.340 --> 19:54.180
Let's drink.

19:58.740 --> 19:59.580
Marshal Duan,

20:00.100 --> 20:01.870
I heard you returned

20:01.870 --> 20:02.710
the marshal's seal.

20:04.580 --> 20:06.500
If you don't want to be the Marshal,

20:06.910 --> 20:08.630
give that seal to me.

20:08.910 --> 20:10.260
I will take the post for you.

20:10.260 --> 20:11.390
Would that not be just fine?

20:11.780 --> 20:12.620
General Wu,

20:12.780 --> 20:13.820
as I told you long ago,

20:14.430 --> 20:15.780
if you chased office in Nandu,

20:16.470 --> 20:17.710
you'd be done for.

20:19.060 --> 20:20.100
Marshal Duan is right.

20:21.580 --> 20:22.710
Right about what?

20:23.910 --> 20:25.670
I was only joking.

20:26.190 --> 20:27.150
I'd never be an official

20:27.150 --> 20:28.190
in Nandu.

20:28.780 --> 20:29.630
I won this land back

20:29.630 --> 20:31.260
with my life.

20:31.710 --> 20:32.580
I wouldn't rest easy

20:32.580 --> 20:33.670
leaving it to others.

20:35.020 --> 20:36.540
Han, say a few words.

20:38.390 --> 20:39.430
General Wu is right.

20:40.630 --> 20:42.100
I've grown used to the frontier.

20:42.910 --> 20:43.896
I can't go anywhere else.

20:49.500 --> 20:50.340
Come, come.

20:50.500 --> 20:51.710
So you've all decided

20:52.870 --> 20:53.710
to stay here?

20:55.630 --> 20:56.470
That's right.

20:56.820 --> 20:57.670
We'll stay to guard

20:57.910 --> 20:58.750
the frontier.

21:03.060 --> 21:03.900
I'll go

21:04.670 --> 21:05.510
where Meng Wan goes.

21:09.100 --> 21:10.190
Han and I

21:10.390 --> 21:11.390
will stand with you two.

21:15.190 --> 21:16.060
Xu, what about you?

21:43.390 --> 21:44.710
The 17 Prefectures are back.

21:46.190 --> 21:47.030
My wish is fulfilled.

21:48.780 --> 21:50.580
Simu and I will wander the realm

21:52.060 --> 21:52.900
and never return.

22:01.190 --> 22:02.030
Xu,

22:03.780 --> 22:05.020
are you truly leaving?

22:20.060 --> 22:21.020
Though we part,

22:24.580 --> 22:25.580
we still share the wind.

23:36.380 --> 23:40.340
(Liang)

23:41.950 --> 23:43.540
Your wishes have all come true.

23:44.430 --> 23:45.870
What will you do now?

23:48.500 --> 23:49.340
Simu,

23:50.910 --> 23:51.910
I had a dream last night.

23:56.500 --> 23:57.340
In that dream,

23:58.230 --> 23:59.376
we lived a life of seclusion.

24:00.340 --> 24:01.296
One cottage, two souls,

24:02.557 --> 24:03.790
three meals, and four seasons.

24:06.670 --> 24:07.510
Seeds in spring,

24:08.150 --> 24:08.990
rain in summer,

24:09.710 --> 24:10.710
chrysanthemums in autumn,

24:11.470 --> 24:12.310
and snow in winter.

24:15.430 --> 24:16.340
Year after year,

24:17.670 --> 24:19.100
we lived a quiet, ordinary life.

24:20.230 --> 24:22.790
♪With the east wind♪

24:25.510 --> 24:28.250
♪In the season at its fullest♪

24:28.260 --> 24:29.366
I want to return to our home

24:33.190 --> 24:34.030
with you.

24:34.690 --> 24:37.500
♪The old night♪

24:39.450 --> 24:46.410
♪Borrow mortal warmth to ease the cold♪

24:47.260 --> 24:48.100
All right.

24:50.390 --> 24:53.910
♪Savoring wine and graceful dances♪

24:54.090 --> 25:00.910
♪Let me love with all my heart
in youthful grace♪

25:01.280 --> 25:09.330
♪With light, carefree words,
still shining bright♪

25:09.670 --> 25:12.570
♪With you by my side♪

25:16.470 --> 25:17.780
It's truly good to be home.

25:18.870 --> 25:20.020
This is my home.

25:21.390 --> 25:22.383
That was a gift from me,

25:23.540 --> 25:24.630
along with myself.

25:26.550 --> 25:27.616
What would you like to eat?

25:27.836 --> 25:29.069
I'll take you to get some food.

25:29.820 --> 25:30.660
Simu,

25:31.150 --> 25:31.990
let's have fish.

25:31.990 --> 25:36.060
♪If you'd let me know how to tell♪

25:37.020 --> 25:38.230
I don't know how to cook fish.

25:38.230 --> 25:39.080
You chose

25:39.090 --> 25:40.190
such tricky ingredients.

25:40.190 --> 25:41.540
Isn't it enough that I can?

25:42.260 --> 25:43.580
We're having a full fish banquet.

25:46.020 --> 25:53.310
♪Borrow mortal warmth to ease the cold♪

25:54.340 --> 25:55.580
It doesn't seem willing.

25:55.710 --> 25:56.670
What a slippery fish.

25:57.470 --> 25:58.310
Simu,

25:58.710 --> 25:59.550
help me scoop it up.

26:01.470 --> 26:02.310
Let's give it a try.

26:04.700 --> 26:07.690
♪In youthful grace♪

26:07.930 --> 26:10.960
♪With light, carefree words♪

26:12.780 --> 26:13.620
Simu,

26:15.500 --> 26:16.630
I like being with you.

26:17.440 --> 26:22.590
♪A pot of wine in fleeting dreams♪

26:24.250 --> 26:32.620
♪A brief life dares seek eternity♪

26:33.410 --> 26:39.410
♪Borrow one lovely dream;
let me savor this fleeting joy♪

26:39.870 --> 26:40.710
Your Grace,

26:41.910 --> 26:42.780
do you still like

26:43.540 --> 26:45.020
my skull as you did

26:46.230 --> 26:47.430
back then?

26:49.780 --> 26:50.620
Yes.

26:51.820 --> 26:52.780
I want to remember you,

26:54.630 --> 26:55.470
your smile,

26:56.990 --> 26:57.870
your scent,

26:59.540 --> 27:00.380
your colors,

27:01.910 --> 27:02.870
and this moment.

27:07.320 --> 27:09.890
♪To what home shall I return♪

27:10.020 --> 27:10.860
Great Ancestor...

27:14.340 --> 27:15.260
Let's go.

27:15.260 --> 27:16.100
Stop there.

27:17.630 --> 27:18.470
Come here.

27:20.780 --> 27:21.740
Great Ancestor,

27:22.100 --> 27:23.060
spare my life.

27:23.670 --> 27:24.510
I...

27:24.670 --> 27:25.710
I have just recovered.

27:26.100 --> 27:27.630
My eyes still have excessive heat,

27:28.230 --> 27:29.260
so they're not so sharp.

27:30.580 --> 27:31.580
I saw nothing at all.

27:33.260 --> 27:35.150
I came to deliver medicine
to General Duan.

27:36.150 --> 27:38.100
I brought all of these

27:38.100 --> 27:38.940
from Starhaven Sect.

27:41.990 --> 27:43.190
I am no longer a general.

27:44.230 --> 27:45.150
Since you're here,

27:45.740 --> 27:46.950
stay for a simple meal.

27:47.190 --> 27:48.030
No, no.

27:48.430 --> 27:50.430
I won't disturb you. Goodbye.

27:50.470 --> 27:51.580
I'll cook today.

27:52.710 --> 27:53.950
Don't you want a taste?

28:09.710 --> 28:10.550
Great Ancestor,

28:11.300 --> 28:13.470
you aren't treating him like a patient,

28:15.580 --> 28:16.820
nor me like a person.

28:17.740 --> 28:19.470
Then starve yourself.

28:46.260 --> 28:47.100
Is it good?

29:03.060 --> 29:03.900
I'll go check on him.

29:10.020 --> 29:11.620
Ziji, sit down and eat.

29:26.060 --> 29:27.020
It's not that bad.

29:28.260 --> 29:29.300
It tastes fine to me.

29:44.500 --> 29:45.340
What's wrong?

29:46.580 --> 29:47.420
Look, look.

29:47.710 --> 29:48.820
It's not that bad, huh?

29:49.390 --> 29:50.340
I only threw up my food.

29:50.340 --> 29:51.320
You're coughing up blood.

29:52.740 --> 29:53.580
How is it?

29:53.820 --> 29:54.800
Do you have any medicine?

29:55.230 --> 29:56.296
- I have some.
- I'm fine.

29:58.340 --> 29:59.280
Which kind do you want?

30:00.260 --> 30:01.100
I'm fine.

30:02.710 --> 30:03.550
However,

30:06.470 --> 30:07.670
I do have one favor to ask.

30:09.580 --> 30:10.420
What do you want?

30:14.580 --> 30:15.420
Come here.

30:16.870 --> 30:17.710
Come closer.

30:25.190 --> 30:26.030
What?

30:26.470 --> 30:27.310
Duan Shunxi.

30:29.020 --> 30:29.860
Duan Shunxi,

30:30.630 --> 30:31.990
I've never

30:31.990 --> 30:32.830
wronged you.

30:32.840 --> 30:33.680
Why must you make me

30:33.680 --> 30:34.560
await my end

30:34.560 --> 30:35.450
before Great Ancestor?

30:49.300 --> 30:50.870
Everything in this world

30:51.430 --> 30:52.870
will one day fade away.

30:54.300 --> 30:55.230
Your Grace,

30:55.990 --> 30:56.896
why force him to stay?

30:59.300 --> 31:00.340
This is his fate.

31:01.300 --> 31:02.150
None of your business.

31:10.060 --> 31:11.190
As the Sovereign of the Void,

31:12.260 --> 31:13.670
you can't stay in the Mortal World.

31:15.100 --> 31:16.100
Go back soon.

31:17.470 --> 31:18.950
Then how much longer will you stay

31:18.950 --> 31:19.910
in this Mortal World,

31:21.670 --> 31:22.510
Immortal?

31:42.430 --> 31:43.270
Duan Shunxi,

31:44.990 --> 31:46.540
you'll leave Great Ancestor.

31:47.780 --> 31:48.820
Aren't you sad?

31:53.950 --> 31:54.790
In all my life,

31:57.150 --> 31:58.540
from first love to my dying day,

32:01.190 --> 32:02.780
I have only loved one girl.

32:07.260 --> 32:08.190
I count myself lucky.

32:10.910 --> 32:11.750
Now,

32:13.710 --> 32:15.580
I don't want my last days in sorrow.

32:21.390 --> 32:22.230
Still,

32:22.670 --> 32:23.990
perhaps when I die,

32:26.540 --> 32:27.630
I'll cling to her and weep.

33:12.470 --> 33:13.310
After I am gone,

33:14.670 --> 33:15.580
will you grieve for me?

33:17.470 --> 33:18.740
Will you hold me and weep too?

33:25.910 --> 33:27.020
All these years,

33:29.100 --> 33:30.670
whenever my death is mentioned,

33:30.780 --> 33:31.990
you say nothing.

33:33.390 --> 33:34.230
How absurd.

33:35.260 --> 33:36.430
What are you running from?

33:38.020 --> 33:39.230
Didn't your kind

33:39.910 --> 33:41.670
set this brief fate

33:42.020 --> 33:43.100
for the Hejia lineage,

33:44.260 --> 33:45.230
Immortal?

33:50.100 --> 33:50.980
You stayed by my side

33:50.980 --> 33:52.260
and read mortals for years.

33:53.060 --> 33:53.900
Now,

33:54.060 --> 33:56.230
do you think your kind was wrong?

33:58.190 --> 33:59.470
Immortals don't err.

34:00.630 --> 34:01.870
Even mortals' right and wrong

34:02.540 --> 34:03.670
are set by immortals.

34:07.710 --> 34:08.550
Yes.

34:08.950 --> 34:09.790
How very clever.

34:10.870 --> 34:12.140
How could immortals be wrong?

34:13.910 --> 34:14.950
Then why did you create

34:14.950 --> 34:15.870
this order

34:15.870 --> 34:16.710
in the first place?

34:17.870 --> 34:19.470
To keep the world in balance

34:20.390 --> 34:21.910
and secure happiness for most.

34:22.020 --> 34:22.860
So,

34:23.220 --> 34:24.060
you have been using

34:24.060 --> 34:24.990
our kindness.

34:25.750 --> 34:26.590
We have upheld

34:26.600 --> 34:27.660
the happiness of the many.

34:27.990 --> 34:29.060
Yet we have no choice

34:29.060 --> 34:30.350
but to suffer for it.

34:30.790 --> 34:31.990
You dress it up in noble words

34:31.990 --> 34:32.950
while tormenting us.

34:34.310 --> 34:35.456
Don't you see your arrogance?

34:37.830 --> 34:38.670
That is

34:39.500 --> 34:40.750
why I have come here.

34:43.500 --> 34:45.310
If you still see no fault in yourself,

34:46.310 --> 34:47.660
go back.

34:49.990 --> 34:50.830
Ziji,

34:51.580 --> 34:52.500
to speak plainly,

34:54.350 --> 34:55.790
I am tired of this game.

35:01.750 --> 35:02.870
(Ten years by your side)

35:03.990 --> 35:04.830
(until this day.)

35:07.540 --> 35:08.470
(Immortal,)

35:10.750 --> 35:11.750
(will you save me?)

35:14.730 --> 35:18.350
♪In silence, I gaze at you♪

35:18.550 --> 35:22.280
♪My hand hangs and then falls♪

35:22.630 --> 35:26.190
♪Let what stays unsaid pass♪

35:27.030 --> 35:30.440
♪Why torture each other like this?♪

35:30.720 --> 35:33.990
♪My wish might be♪

35:35.060 --> 35:35.900
Ziji,

35:38.100 --> 35:39.270
you grabbed me.

35:39.760 --> 35:44.100
♪They fade like a dream♪

35:45.750 --> 35:49.610
♪Daylight fades into ash♪

35:50.540 --> 35:52.259
(It's been over a month
since your letter.)

35:53.220 --> 35:55.020
(Are you and Miss He both well?)

35:59.100 --> 35:59.950
(Somehow,)

36:00.910 --> 36:02.270
(I often dream)

36:02.270 --> 36:04.220
(of our childhood days in Daizhou.)

36:04.540 --> 36:06.820
(Daizhou)

36:08.470 --> 36:14.340
♪Collapse piece by piece♪

36:16.700 --> 36:19.550
♪I hate that I hesitated♪

36:19.550 --> 36:21.910
(Yet old days will fade like mist.)

36:21.910 --> 36:24.280
(Erudite and Determined)

36:24.280 --> 36:26.270
♪Leaving all behind♪

36:26.310 --> 36:27.950
(I have found what I wish to do.)

36:28.580 --> 36:29.620
(For now, all is well.)

36:32.870 --> 36:34.700
(Though the moon may wax and wane,)

36:35.790 --> 36:37.310
(I still wish that you and Miss He)

36:37.620 --> 36:38.740
(can be as full as the moon)

36:39.700 --> 36:40.790
(and live a happy life.)

36:41.910 --> 36:43.950
(Your sister, Jingyuan, respectfully)

37:02.860 --> 37:06.020
(Your sister, Jingyuan, respectfully)

37:07.130 --> 37:10.640
♪Let memories drift away♪

37:11.010 --> 37:13.680
♪Alone, I gather them up♪

37:13.890 --> 37:18.340
♪Like petals in the spring sun♪

37:18.640 --> 37:22.200
♪Till the past falls still again♪

37:22.560 --> 37:26.120
♪And turns to clear daylight♪

37:26.310 --> 37:34.700
♪The wind returns with my dreams♪

37:56.390 --> 37:57.680
Will you send Jingyuan a reply?

38:00.470 --> 38:02.060
She's found what she wants to do

38:03.270 --> 38:04.430
and started a new life.

38:05.660 --> 38:07.060
I won't give her more to worry over.

38:13.750 --> 38:14.590
Jingyuan mentioned

38:14.590 --> 38:15.830
those days back in Daizhou.

38:20.020 --> 38:20.860
I think

38:22.990 --> 38:24.310
she cared for Xianye.

38:27.731 --> 38:28.965
If the time they spent together

38:28.976 --> 38:29.670
had been longer,

38:31.870 --> 38:32.710
perhaps...

38:44.399 --> 38:45.512
Maybe this is for the best.

38:48.430 --> 38:49.830
She should soon forget

38:52.430 --> 38:53.950
a brief, hazy memory.

38:57.390 --> 38:58.500
How could she forget?

39:00.140 --> 39:00.980
She will not.

39:08.470 --> 39:10.180
Jingyuan wished us full as the moon.

39:12.433 --> 39:14.079
Yet we're here,
and the full moon is not.

39:16.953 --> 39:17.950
It's been so long since I

39:17.950 --> 39:18.993
admired the moon with you.

39:21.790 --> 39:22.790
The Mid-Autumn Festival

39:24.470 --> 39:25.500
is too far away.

39:26.986 --> 39:28.492
If you want to celebrate the festival,

39:28.620 --> 39:29.470
we can do it anytime.

39:31.060 --> 39:31.900
But if you want

39:33.430 --> 39:34.620
to admire the moon...

39:39.350 --> 39:40.190
Wait for a moment.

41:27.910 --> 41:28.750
Simu.

41:30.897 --> 41:32.917
The moonlight beneath the sun
is beautiful, right?

41:37.700 --> 41:38.540
Do you like it?

41:39.660 --> 41:40.500
I do.

41:42.060 --> 41:43.020
I always do.

42:10.680 --> 42:16.010
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

42:16.340 --> 42:20.590
♪Light encountered shadow♪

42:21.950 --> 42:27.320
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

42:27.620 --> 42:32.220
♪The unbreakable fate♪

42:33.310 --> 42:35.150
♪Suddenly cracked♪

42:47.360 --> 42:52.800
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

42:52.980 --> 42:57.310
♪Light encountered shadow♪

42:58.680 --> 43:04.070
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

43:04.300 --> 43:08.240
♪The unbreakable fate♪

43:10.010 --> 43:11.900
♪Suddenly cracked♪

43:14.560 --> 43:17.720
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

43:17.720 --> 43:20.250
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

43:20.250 --> 43:25.770
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

43:25.770 --> 43:29.010
♪Following fate's guidance♪

43:29.010 --> 43:33.870
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

43:34.210 --> 43:37.230
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

43:37.230 --> 43:40.050
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

43:40.310 --> 43:42.840
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

43:42.840 --> 43:48.260
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

43:48.430 --> 43:51.500
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

43:51.660 --> 43:56.560
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

43:56.770 --> 44:00.240
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
